      <title>瑞士政府反对限制人口的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/swiss-government-says-it-s-against-proposal-to-cap-population</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府反对将国家人口限制在 1000 万的提议，称此举危及经济增长和安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/swiss-government-says-it-s-against-proposal-to-cap-population</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
